name: Transhuman Immortals 2.0
description: Transhumanism: noun - the belief or theory that the human race can evolve beyond its current physical and mental limitations, especially by means of science and technology. Can we reach immortality? Will we expand our life expectancy? Will we live longer, healthier lives with the help of medical technology such as gene editing? Only time will tell. By @dehiscenceart, January 20, 2022.
